        <td bgcolor='black' valign=top width='100' nowrap><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'><b>zikuofkarana</b></font></td>
        <td bgcolor='black' valign='top' width='100%'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> can anyone tell me about thur gate potions? like how to make them, where to farm the stuff? im bound in the firepot room, and getting to thurg is a pain....im a lazy necro, what can i say.</P><P>plus, i hate paying droods for ports</P><P>or can you point me to a website that tells me where the stuff all drops or anything, please?</P><P>thanks in advance</P><P> </font></td>
